        <title>Vim配置为IDE之踩坑记录</title>
        <link>https://cc922.github.io/p/vim%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BAide%E4%B9%8B%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</link>
